    "KasetPlus creates fresh AI sessions per request. Refresh the status if Apple Intelligence finishes downloading or becomes available while the app is open." : {
      "comment" : "Settings window → Intelligence tab (on-device Apple Intelligence features: AI command bar, playlist refinement, lyrics explanations).",
