    "Open the command bar to control music with natural language. Try saying \"play something chill\" or \"add jazz to queue\"." : {
      "comment" : "Help text for the AI command bar in Intelligence settings.",
      "localizations" : {
        "af" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Open the command bar to control music with natural language. Try saying \"play something chill\" or \"add jazz to queue\"."
          }
        },
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "افتح شريط الأوامر للتحكم في الموسيقى باللغة الطبيعية. جرّب قول \"play something chill\" أو \"add jazz to queue\"."
          }
        },
        "ca" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Open the command bar to control music with natural language. Try saying \"play something chill\" or \"add jazz to queue\"."
          }
        },
        "cs" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Otevřete příkazový řádek a ovládejte hudbu přirozeným jazykem. Zkuste říct \"něco chill\" nebo \"přidat jazz do fronty\"."
          }
        },
        "da" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Åbn kommando bar til at styre musik med naturligt sprog. Prøv at sige \"spille noget chill\" eller \"tilføje jazz til køen\"."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Öffne die Befehlsleiste, um Musik mit natürlicher Sprache zu steuern. Versuche zum Beispiel \"play something chill\" oder \"add jazz to queue\"."
          }
        },
        "el" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ανοίξτε τη γραμμή εντολών για να ελέγξετε τη μουσική με τη φυσική γλώσσα. Προσπαθήστε να πείτε \"παίξτε κάτι τσιγάρο\" ή \"προσθέστε τζαζ στην ουρά\"."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Abre la barra de comandos para controlar la música con lenguaje natural. Prueba a decir \"play something chill\" o \"add jazz to queue\"."
          }
        },
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Avaa komentorivi ohjataksesi musiikkia luonnollisella kielellä. Yritä sanoa \"soita jotain vilkasta\" tai \"lisää jazzia jonoon\"."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ouvrez la barre de commandes pour contrôler la musique en langage naturel. Essayez par exemple \"play something chill\" ou \"add jazz to queue\"."
          }
        },
        "he" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Open the command bar to control music with natural language. Try saying \"play something chill\" or \"add jazz to queue\"."
          }
        },
        "hu" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Open the command bar to control music with natural language. Try saying \"play something chill\" or \"add jazz to queue\"."
          }
        },
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Buka Command Bar untuk mengontrol musik dengan bahasa alami. Coba ucapkan \"play something chill\" atau \"add jazz to queue\"."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Apri la barra dei comandi per controllare la musica in linguaggio naturale. Prova a dire \"play something chill\" o \"add jazz to queue\"."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "自然言語で音楽をコントロールするには、コマンドバーを開きます。「何か冷たい」または「ジャズをキューに追加」と言ってみてください。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "자연어로 음악을 제어하려면 명령 막대를 여세요. \"play something chill\" 또는 \"add jazz to queue\"라고 말해 보세요."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Open de opdrachtbalk om muziek met natuurlijke taal te bedienen. Probeer bijvoorbeeld \"play something chill\" of \"add jazz to queue\"."
          }
        },
        "no" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Åpne kommandolinjen for å styre musikk med naturlig språk. Prøv å si \"spill noe kjøl\" eller \"legg til jazz i kø\"."
          }
        },
        "pl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Otwórz pasek poleceń, aby sterować muzyką językiem naturalnym. Spróbuj powiedzieć \"play something chill\" albo \"add jazz to queue\"."
          }
        },
        "pt" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Abra a barra de comandos para controlar a música com linguagem natural. Experimente dizer \"play something chill\" ou \"add jazz to queue\"."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Abra a barra de comando para controlar músicas com linguagem natural. Tente dizer \"toque algo frio\" ou \"adicione jazz à fila\"."
          }
        },
        "ro" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Deschideți bara de comandă pentru a controla muzica cu un limbaj natural. Încercați să spuneți \"cântați ceva frig\" sau \"adăugați jazz la coadă\"."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Откройте панель команд, чтобы управлять музыкой естественным языком. Попробуйте сказать \"play something chill\" или \"add jazz to queue\"."
          }
        },
        "sr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Open the command bar to control music with natural language. Try saying \"play something chill\" or \"add jazz to queue\"."
          }
        },
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Öppna kommandofältet för att styra musik med naturligt språk. Prova att säga \"play something chill\" eller \"add jazz to queue\"."
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Müziği doğal dille kontrol etmek için Komut Çubuğu'nu açın. \"play something chill\" veya \"add jazz to queue\" demeyi deneyin."
          }
        },
        "uk" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Відкрийте панель команд, щоб керувати музикою природною мовою. Спробуйте сказати \"play something chill\" або \"add jazz to queue\"."
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Open the command bar to control music with natural language. Try saying \"play something chill\" or \"add jazz to queue\"."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "打开命令栏以控制自然语言的音乐。请尝试说\"播放一个棋子\"或\"添加jazz到队列\"。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Open the command bar to control music with natural language. Try saying \"play something chill\" or \"add jazz to queue\"."
          }
        }
      }
    },
