    "The command bar stays available even if Apple Intelligence is off, with AI enhancing only the richer interpretations and summaries." : {
      "comment" : "Settings window → Intelligence tab (on-device Apple Intelligence features: AI command bar, playlist refinement, lyrics explanations).",
      "localizations" : {
        "af" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "The command bar stays available even if Apple Intelligence is off, with AI enhancing only the richer interpretations and summaries."
          }
        },
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "يبقى شريط الأوامر متاحًا حتى إذا كان Apple Intelligence متوقفًا، حيث يعزّز الذكاء الاصطناعي فقط التفسيرات والملخصات الأكثر ثراءً."
          }
        },
        "ca" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "The command bar stays available even if Apple Intelligence is off, with AI enhancing only the richer interpretations and summaries."
          }
        },
        "cs" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Příkazová lišta zůstává k dispozici i v případě, že Apple Intelligence skončí, a AI zlepšuje pouze bohatší interpretace a shrnutí."
          }
        },
        "da" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Kommandolinjen forbliver tilgængelig, selvom Apple Intelligence er slukket, med AI øge kun de rigere fortolkninger og resuméer."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Die Befehlsleiste bleibt auch dann verfügbar, wenn Apple Intelligence deaktiviert ist. KI verbessert dann nur umfangreichere Interpretationen und Zusammenfassungen."
          }
        },
        "el" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Η γραμμή εντολών παραμένει διαθέσιμη ακόμη και αν η Apple Intelligence είναι απενεργοποιημένη, με AI ενίσχυση μόνο τις πλουσιότερες ερμηνείες και περιλήψεις."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "La barra de comandos sigue disponible aunque Apple Intelligence esté desactivado; la IA solo mejora las interpretaciones y los resúmenes más avanzados."
          }
        },
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Komentopalkki pysyy käytettävissä, vaikka Apple Intelligence olisi pois päältä, ja tekoäly parantaisi vain rikkaampia tulkintoja ja yhteenvetoja."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "La barre de commandes reste disponible même si Apple Intelligence est désactivé, l'IA n'améliorant que les interprétations et résumés plus riches."
          }
        },
        "he" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "The command bar stays available even if Apple Intelligence is off, with AI enhancing only the richer interpretations and summaries."
          }
        },
        "hu" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "The command bar stays available even if Apple Intelligence is off, with AI enhancing only the richer interpretations and summaries."
          }
        },
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Command Bar tetap tersedia meskipun Apple Intelligence dimatikan, dengan AI hanya meningkatkan interpretasi dan ringkasan yang lebih kaya."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "La barra dei comandi resta disponibile anche se Apple Intelligence è disattivato, con l'IA che migliora solo le interpretazioni e i riepiloghi più ricchi."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "コマンドバーは、Apple Intelligenceがオフの場合でも利用可能であり、AIはより豊かな解釈と要約のみを強化します。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Apple Intelligence가 꺼져 있어도 명령 막대는 계속 사용할 수 있으며, AI는 더 풍부한 해석과 요약만 향상합니다."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "De opdrachtbalk blijft beschikbaar, zelfs als Apple Intelligence uit staat; AI verbetert dan alleen rijkere interpretaties en samenvattingen."
          }
        },
        "no" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Kommandolinjen forblir tilgjengelig selv om Apple Intelligence er avslått, med AI som bare forbedrer rikerens tolkninger og oppsummeringer."
          }
        },
        "pl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pasek poleceń pozostaje dostępny nawet wtedy, gdy Apple Intelligence jest wyłączone, a SI ulepsza jedynie bogatsze interpretacje i podsumowania."
          }
        },
        "pt" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "A barra de comandos continua disponível mesmo que o Apple Intelligence esteja desativado, com a IA a melhorar apenas as interpretações e resumos mais ricos."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "A barra de comando permanece disponível, mesmo que a Apple Intelligence esteja desligada, e apenas melhore as interpretações e resumos mais ricos."
          }
        },
        "ro" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bara de comandă rămâne disponibilă chiar dacă Apple Intelligence este oprit, cu AI îmbunătățind doar interpretările și rezumatele mai bogate."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Панель команд остаётся доступной даже при выключенном Apple Intelligence, а ИИ лишь улучшает более сложные интерпретации и сводки."
          }
        },
        "sr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "The command bar stays available even if Apple Intelligence is off, with AI enhancing only the richer interpretations and summaries."
          }
        },
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Kommandofältet förblir tillgängligt även om Apple Intelligence är avstängt, och AI förbättrar då bara fylligare tolkningar och sammanfattningar."
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Apple Intelligence kapalı olsa bile Komut Çubuğu kullanılabilir kalır; yapay zeka yalnızca daha zengin yorumları ve özetleri geliştirir."
          }
        },
        "uk" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Панель команд залишається доступною навіть коли Apple Intelligence вимкнено, а ШІ лише покращує змістовніші інтерпретації та підсумки."
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "The command bar stays available even if Apple Intelligence is off, with AI enhancing only the richer interpretations and summaries."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "即使Apple Intelligence 关闭，命令栏也仍然可以使用，而大赦国际只能加强较丰富的解释和摘要。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "The command bar stays available even if Apple Intelligence is off, with AI enhancing only the richer interpretations and summaries."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The equalizer activates as soon as you press play." : {
