    "When enabled, you can use natural language commands, AI-powered playlist refinement, and lyrics explanations." : {
      "comment" : "Description of the Apple Intelligence master toggle in Intelligence settings.",
      "localizations" : {
        "af" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "When enabled, you can use natural language commands, AI-powered playlist refinement, and lyrics explanations."
